      In internal/role/{dispatcher,tmux}.go, write the selected provider's
      base_url + role model into the generated opencode.json and inject the
      api_key_env-resolved value into the agent process environment.
      Fail dispatch fast when api_key_env is unset/empty or base_url is
      unreachable. No changes to the web UI (provider config is operator-only).
