**Feature Branch**: `crud-feature`

**Created**: 2026-06-26
---ACCEPTANCE---
# Acceptance Criteria ‚Äî Feature CRUD (Edit & Delete)

Every criterion follows Given/When/Then with a test level and a specific verification method. Criteria are grouped by user story and constraint.

## User Story 1 ‚Äî Edit Title & Priority
