# Acceptance Criteria: crud-feature

Every user story has at least one acceptance criterion per relevant test level. API changes ‚Üí smoke + integration. UI changes ‚Üí smoke + integration + e2e. State-machine guards ‚Üí unit. Error paths ‚Üí one criterion per error scenario.

