+|-----------|--------|-----------|
+| I. Spec-Driven, Always | Compliant | This spec precedes any implementation; spec.md + acceptance.md + repos.yaml produced before planning. |
+| II. Six Roles, Fixed Pipeline | Compliant | Feature changes how a role's agent is dispatched, not the pipeline order or role set. No role skipped/reordered. |
+| III. Central Spec, Distributed Implementation | Compliant | Single spec in the devteam repo; repos.yaml declares scope (devteam repo only). No spec duplication. |
+| IV. Two Intake Paths, One Output Format | Compliant | Loose-idea intake; output is the standard spec.md + acceptance.md + repos.yaml shape. |
