---
name: devteam
description: Manage the Dev Team multi-agent platform ‚Äî an AIDLC pipeline orchestrator that runs features through inception, planning, construction, review, testing, and delivery phases using agent dispatch. Use when working with the Dev Team CLI (devteam command), managing features, running pipeline phases, checking status, or operating the web UI. Triggers on "devteam", "dev team", "pipeline status", "feature status", "run phase", "gate check", or any question about the Dev Team platform.
